The fiber of formula_107 over a point formula_110 consists of the pairs formula_111 where formula_112 is a path from formula_113 to formula_104, i.e. the loop space formula_80. The inclusion formula_116 of the fiber of formula_107 into the homotopy fiber of formula_107 is again a homotopy equivalence and iteration yields the sequence:formula_119Due to the duality of fibration and cofibration, there also exists a sequence of cofibrations. These two sequences are known as the Puppe sequences or the sequences of fibrations and cofibrations.

== Principal fibration ==
A fibration formula_1 with fiber formula_93 is called principal, if there exists a commutative diagram:

The bottom row is a sequence of fibrations and the vertical mappings are weak homotopy equivalences. Principal fibrations play an important role in Postnikov towers.

